{"tid":1574424,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[幫手推]921討論","createTime":"2019-09-16T11:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T06:01:12.000Z","uid":241525,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"697522ad547227e8126d3dc72b668a59454b64f7","tid":1574424,"uid":241525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:55:28.000Z","msg":"依家講921好似早咗啲<br />\n但我想早小小傾 俾啲時間大家去準備<br />\n而且對家有唒準備 我地就冇傾過921<br />\n<br />\n何妖就講明921有18區清潔行動<br />\n假設佢係揾人清連儂牆<br />\n咁我地應唔應該還拖守牆<br />\n定係照舊撕一貼百<br />\n同埋921 元朗有靜坐 <br />\n班牛屎佬實會搞鳩靜坐手足<br />\n<br />\n所以小弟認為住係大西北嘅手足全部同我去元朗<br />\n而各區連儂牆可以等各區街坊去守<br />\n屌狗咁樣屌走班藍絲清潔工<br />\n而九龍嘅手足都可以留守反自己嗰區<br />\n以防有啲藍絲暴徒 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"41b5dddb4c336ffa6bb87831fda560eeecae2570","tid":1574424,"uid":241525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:55:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8fa46f83e740476023e53eecb28e9a9d212096ae","tid":1574424,"uid":241525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:55:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e35bf1ae2eb85fb8a8b6f6df6f8ae79470e46118","tid":1574424,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:56:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwith